{"tid":672800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遇襲紋身漢闖校求救","createTime":"2018-05-21T09:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T10:28:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"35132f0b9959858b9597dee07e1d25b1b0163af9","tid":672800,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T09:55:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397025\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397025&d=udWQ8CAbBnyBdUhumdbJwEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f9e7f69a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F20397025&h=f31cf7e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180521/20397025</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月21日 <br />\n<br />\n遇襲紋身漢闖校求救<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180521/large/21la7p06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180521%2Flarge%2F21la7p06.jpg&h=f014f447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■受傷男子身中至少三刀被送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名紋身漢昨早在大角嘴街頭遇伏擊，頭頸身中刀受創，負傷逃命200多米闖進一間學校求救，剛巧該校被醫療輔助隊借用場地進行活動，隊員立即替傷者急救，再召救護車將他送院，事主經治理後情況穩定。警方列傷人案，正追查兇徒下落及調查犯案動機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巧遇醫療輔助隊練習<br />\n<br />\n現場位於大角嘴詩歌舞街一間學校，周日原僅校工在場，不過剛巧醫療輔助隊昨早借用場地進行急救練習，多名隊員在校內訓練。遇襲受傷男子姓卓，37歲，上身有紋身。<br />\n<br />\n據悉昨早9時許，卓在醫局街137號深水埗公立醫局美沙酮診所外遭一名男子持刀伏擊，他頭頸身至少中3刀，負傷且戰且退，走至200多米外的校門，當時學校並無上鎖，卓推門而進高聲呼救，在場醫療輔助隊員見狀，立即為他包紮止血及報警。<br />\n<br />\n救護車接報趕至，將傷者送往伊利沙伯醫院，經治理後情況穩定。警方到場封鎖學校，沿途步至美沙酮診所外街頭搜證，現場遺下一條血路。警方正調查施襲者動機，翻看附近大廈閉路電視追緝兇徒，案件列作傷人。<br />\n<br />\n■記者文兆麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n私家車旺角鏟路四傷<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n泛民建制防𠝹票　李鳳琼　植潔鈴與陳真真劃清界線"},{"pid":"ede11e03c155ac61b3b4ffcee078d55100aa133a","tid":672800,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"大難不死系列<br />\n探病時間再來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d8b14ddc63d6443088303bb55fba639e415090","tid":672800,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:20:23.000Z","msg":"撞啱急救班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b1148311bf88621836386c967e780d44ad19db","tid":672800,"uid":25148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:23:59.000Z","msg":"遇襲受傷男子姓卓，37歲，上身有紋身。<br />\n你話佢戴粗金鏈 有吸煙習慣都得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係都要寫到咁令人有聯想既"},{"pid":"746a14e263d4d255dc2bb77bd8556e89155e7ade","tid":672800,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:25:36.000Z","msg":"佢都算大命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be50d0e41d2112d5fea4c5cfc6186906f3e89e86","tid":672800,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"746a14e263d4d255dc2bb77bd8556e89155e7ade","tid":672800,"uid":13090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:25:36.000Z","msg":"佢都算大命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"仲要好好運<br />\n班人係識急救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}